---
import Linkedin from "@/icons/linkedin.astro";
import IconGithub from "@/icons/IconGitHub.astro";
import IconCoffe from "@/icons/IconCoffe.astro";
---

<footer id="footer" class="w-full md:max-w-6xl mx-auto md:p-8 text-sm py-2 text-white">
  <nav class="flex flex-col gap-8 items-center">

    <!-- Cafecito -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center max-w-md">
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-md leading-relaxed">
        Si mi trabajo te resultó útil o simplemente querés apoyar lo que hago,
        podés invitarme un cafecito. <span class="text-white/80">Cada contribución me ayuda a seguir
        creando proyectos y herramientas de código abierto.</span>
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://cafecito.app/gabyaguero"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="relative flex items-center gap-2.5 px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full
          border border-orange-400/70 bg-orange-500/15 text-orange-300
          shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(251,146,60,0.25)]
          hover:bg-orange-500/25 hover:border-orange-400 hover:text-orange-200
          hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(251,146,60,0.4)]
          transition-all duration-300 font-mono text-[0.75rem]
          animate-pulse"
      >
        <IconCoffe class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" />
        Cafecito
      </a>
    </div>
    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="border-b border-white/[0.08] w-full" />

    <!-- Social links -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 justify-center items-center">
      <a
        class="py-2 border-2 border-slate-700 px-10 hover:border-amber-400 transition-colors duration-300 hover:animate-pulse flex gap-2 items-center rounded-lg"
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriel-aguero-dev/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        <Linkedin class="w-5 h-5" />
        <span>LinkedIn</span>
      </a>
      <a
        class="py-2 border-2 border-slate-700 px-10 hover:border-amber-400 transition-colors duration-300 hover:animate-pulse flex gap-2 items-center rounded-lg"
        href="https://github.com/Gabriel-Aguero"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        <IconGithub class="w-5 h-5" />
        <span>GitHub</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="border-b border-white/[0.08] w-full" />

    <!-- Copyright -->
    <small class="text-orange-300 font-mono text-[0.7rem] tracking-wider">
      Creado por Gabriel Agüero — Frontend Developer
    </small>

  </nav>
</footer>